<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="world-n">world <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wɜːld/    美 /wɜːrld/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>世界；地球：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>people all around/over, the worl<strong>all over the world</strong>
全世界人民</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>全世界的人：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The moment the 28th Olympic Games were declared open, the whole world cheered. 
当宣布第28届奥运会开幕时，全世界都为之欢呼雀跃。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>界；领域：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the newspaper / academic world
报界/学术界</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>社会；生活；生活圈子：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When she lost her son, her <strong>entire world</strong> changed. 
自从失去儿子以后，她的整个世界完全改变了。</p></div>

<h3 id="beon-top-of-the-world">（be）on top of the world非常快乐/幸福</h3>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-the-world">in the world</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>[强调最高级] 在全世界：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have the greatest job in the world.
我拥有世界上最好的工作。</p><footer>人教⑥ – 6</footer></div>

<p>2.★ <strong>[加强语气] 究竟：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her eyes glaring, she shouted, “What in the world were you thinking?”
她瞪着眼睛喊道：“你究竟在想什么？”</p><footer>2010 浙江</footer></div></div>